job_description:
Role- Data Scientist
Job Description
Need Both theoretical and practical idea about basic data science algorithms of Regressing, Clustering, Classification, Natural Language processing, Deep Learning, time series forecasting. Also, must have a clear idea about the applicability of those.
Should be very through about the deep learning concepts of CNN, RNN, Transformer models
Should be able to create chain of serverless multimodal architecture, consisting of many AI models in the chain
Must be strong in python programming, Model training and testing
Must know one of the ML OPS technology either of the following Cloud Offering Azure, AWS or Google
